Preconfigured Claude skills and agents. Meant for my own personal use. Skills, agents, etc... are very opinonated and not meant to be generic.

Inspired by (and some content copied from):

- https://github.com/ChrisWiles/claude-code-showcase
- https://github.com/diet103/claude-code-infrastructure-showcase
- https://github.com/basher83/lunar-claude/blob/main/plugins/infrastructure/ansible-workflows/skills/ansible-fundamentals/SKILL.md

To install or use the plugins:
/plugin marketplace add jbaranski/jeff-claude
/plugin install jeff-plugin-typescript@jeff-plugins
/plugin install jeff-plugin-angular@jeff-plugins
/plugin install jeff-plugin-python@jeff-plugins
/plugin install jeff-plugin-aws-solution-architect@jeff-plugins
/plugin install jeff-plugin-golang@jeff-plugins
